trans-unit.resname: This link is not available anymore!
trans-unit.source: This link is not available anymore!

trans-unit.resname: This link is going to be destroyed once you open it, so please be carefull by clicking on the "Continue" button.
trans-unit.source: This link is going to be destroyed once you open it, so please be carefull by clicking on the "Continue" button.
trans-unit.target: Ce lien sera détruit une fois ouvert donc soyez prudent en cliquant sur "Continuer".

trans-unit.resname: Once you click the "Continue" button, you are going to get the content in read only, you can of course copy it as any text.
trans-unit.source: Once you click the "Continue" button, you are going to get the content in read only, you can of course copy it as any text.
trans-unit.target: Dès que vous aurez cliqué sur le bouton "Continuer vous aurez accès au contenu en lecture seule. Vous pourrez bien sur copier ce dernier comme n'importe quel texte.

trans-unit.resname: Now you can click the "Continue" button if you still want it.
trans-unit.source: Now you can click the "Continue" button if you still want it.
trans-unit.target: Maintenant vous pouvez cliquer sur "Continuer" si vous le souhaitez toujours..

trans-unit.resname: The link containing your content can be opened only one time, then it's destroyed.
trans-unit.source: The link containing your content can be opened only one time, then it's destroyed.
trans-unit.target: Le lien contenant votre contenu ne pourra être ouvert qu'une seule fois.

trans-unit.resname: Even us can't get it back for you.
trans-unit.source: Even us can't get it back for you.
trans-unit.target: Même nous ne pouvons pas récupérer ce contenu une fois lu.
